>Description:
I saw this suggestion on the mailing list:

You might try disabling the colors in the preferences dialog "Editing >
General > Color syntax interactively".

and since the OP really only wanted to PRINT in black-and-white, and not have his interactive session be in black and white, I thought, "Maybe this [black-and-white] could be a printing preference in DrScheme."  Or maybe that's too platform-dependent?
